"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-paris-olympics-2024-rowing-schedule-uk-start-time-dates-b1172461.html\", \"text\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies. Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search. See our privacy policy for more information.  Sport|Olympics  Therowingworld descends on the Vaires-sur-Marne Nautical Stadium to compete for Olympic glory over eight days of action atParis 2024.  There are set to be 502 athletes competing across 14 different events, with the schedule brought to a close by the men's and women's eight finals on August 3.  Team GB have enjoyed plenty of rowing success in the past but the Tokyo Games failed to deliver in the same way, as the British rowers registered their worst Olympic performance in 49 years.  Only two medals were won, silver in the men's quadruple sculls\\u00a0and men's eight bronze. However hopes are high heading into theParis Olympics-  the men's eight crew are the reigning world champions and the women's four, includingHelen Glover, arrive in France in superb form.  Here is the full 2024 Olympics rowing schedule (all times BST)...  08:00:Men's single sculls heats  09:12:Women's single sculls heats  10:30:Men's double sculls heats  11:00:Women's double sculls heats  11:30:Men's quadruple sculls heats  11:50:Women's double sculls heats  08:00:Women's single sculls repechages  08:36:Men's single sculls repechages  09:10:Women's double sculls repechages  09:20:Men's single sculls repechages  09:30:Women's pair heats  10:00:Men's pair heats  10:30:Lightweight women's double sculls heats  11:00:Lightweight men's double sculls heats  11:30:Women's four heats  11:50:Men's four heats  08:30:Men's singles sculls semi-final (E/F)  08:54:Women's singles sculls semi-final (E/F)  09:20:Men's pair repechages  09:30:Women's pair repechages  09:40:Lightweight men's double sculls repechages  10:00:Lightweight women's do